title: Welcome to Dexter’s IS415-GAA
text:
I am Dexter Wan, a final year Computer Science student from SMU. I specialise in cyber security, and have experienced interning at Synapxe under their Policy, Risk and Capability Development (PRCD) team.
This webpage is to document the exercises done for IS415 - Geospatial Analytics and Applications.
